data.description: Look at the most recent updates new SS appliances, cabinet hardware, backsplash, new granite countertops, with under-mount sinks, and new faucets.  A mixture of tile and laminate in the living areas with carpet in the bedrooms.  A multi-functional area upstairs separates the master from the other bedrooms. A large master bedroom, and bath with double sinks and a big walk in closet.  Oil bronze fans, lights, and knobs installed throughout. An extra room off the living area.  Additional features include a sprinkler system, covered patio, gutters, two new garage doors with separate openers, and two HVAC systems. This property sits on a large corner lot in a community that offers a swimming pool and walking trails.
